column3: Im an extrovert who wants to meet new people, date, an enjoy someones company! Its been awhile since Ive even been out in the dating world so I thought I'd give this site a shot :) plus having new friends too isn't a bad thing, new to lakewood anyways.

So far my life has been a constant move. I finally have settled down slightly. Still unsure if i want to stay in lakewood.....

I work a lot, but am mostly available in the evenings. But that also leaves me little to meet people. If someone matters to me ill make as much time as i possibly can to be near them, or at least try to talk to them each evening.

I'm an illustrater, I'm very crafty and can make almost anything, and I create clothes and accessories. I can cook (to a point....not perfect) and I'm really good at being a wifey-in-training XD (aka I like cleaning, cooking, and doteing on my other half)

How to make myself happy

It can change depending on the day. I can be anything from partying it up, or snuggling under covers with a good movie.

Only message me if you are looking for:
Someone to hang with
Not clingy
More than sex -_- (thats a bonus if i like you enough)
And wants to put effort to talk
short & long term dating and new friends
Hesitant, but I'd certainly consider it.
Yes, I'd be playing with them.
